snippet.title: Towelket 4 - Ocean  (no commentary playthrough) 1/2
snippet.description:
part 1: https://youtu.be/jE0k3r7QlIA
part 2: https://youtu.be/6g9M1CtuCrI

WARNING: this game contains graphic and disturbing content. There are scenes depicting violence and blood.

Towelket 4 ~ Ocean ~ is a freeware, story-heavy adventure/role-playing game made in RPG MAKER 2000 by Kanashimi Hocchikisu. It is the sequel to Towelket Reverse, which was later remade as "Towelket 6".
